name: RGB GLITCH Pranksy Rock X/10,000
description:
This NFT offers you absolutely nothing, it's a RGB picture of a rock with a stencil filter & some words in print clearly font. It's also fully animated with subtle movement throughout.

However it has a 10,000 Limit, and is priced at 8 TEZ.

If you for some reason purchase this piece it unlocks a surprise that holds no value beyond a smile
